32
00:03:05,246 --> 00:03:06,876
- Itu dia.
- Ini ceritamu.

33
00:03:06,966 --> 00:03:08,676
[Jantungnya tiba-tiba mulai berdebar,]

34
00:03:08,506 --> 00:03:12,246
{\an8}[Dam]

35
00:03:08,766 --> 00:03:10,656
[dia kesulitan bernapas,]

36
00:03:10,746 --> 00:03:14,226
[lalu merasa pusing seperti berjalan
di awan. Apa artinya ini?]

37
00:03:12,335 --> 00:03:16,156
{\an8}[Dam]

38
