42
00:03:24,516 --> 00:03:25,706
Aku... Aku minta maaf.

43
00:03:28,916 --> 00:03:30,326
[Kapan kau... Tidak, tunggu.]

44
00:03:30,416 --> 00:03:34,286
[Kapan temanmu memiliki perasaan itu?]

45
00:03:34,116 --> 00:03:39,696
{\an8}[Soo-kyung]

46
00:03:36,486 --> 00:03:39,566
[Dia baru saja bersama seseorang.]

47
00:03:40,666 --> 00:03:42,256
[Menurutku,]

48
00:03:43,486 --> 00:03:46,436
[kurasa temanmu jatuh cinta
kepada orang itu.]

49
00:03:48,416 --> 00:03:51,316
{\an8}[Dam]

50
00:03:48,546 --> 00:03:50,306
[Tidak mungkin.]

51
00:03:51,226 --> 00:03:53,336
Kau bilang itu temanmu.
Bagaimana kau tahu?

52
00:03:51,406 --> 00:03:55,095
{\an8}[Jae-jin]

53
00:03:53,696 --> 00:03:55,095
[Karena...]

54
00:03:55,186 --> 00:03:57,566
{\an8}[Jae-jin]

55
00:04:16,966 --> 00:04:18,466
Baiklah.

56
00:04:32,896 --> 00:04:34,696
[Lihat.]

57
00:04:36,676 --> 00:04:40,506
[Aku membakar tempat ini hari ini
untuk bersumpah mati di laut.]

58
00:04:41,076 --> 00:04:43,546
Jika ingin hidup, aku akan mati.

59
00:04:43,626 --> 00:04:46,136
Tapi jika ingin mati, aku akan hidup.

60
00:04:46,226 --> 00:04:48,776
Astaga, dialog itu
selalu membuatku berdebar.

61
00:04:50,226 --> 00:04:54,546
[Tunggu, mungkin jantungku mulai berdebar
